o deducted a point in the final round.\", \"from\": 327, \"to\": 443, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 327, \"end\": 337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Briton\", \"score\": 0.9999999999679403, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Briton\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q25379\", \"Q234460\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Briton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Briton\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for latest news on the Paris Olympics  But ringside judges awarded the victory to Rygielska, stunning Eccles and drawing boos from the crowd.\", \"from\": 445, \"to\": 617, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 578, \"end\": 584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eccles_Line\", \"score\": 0.9999999551816937, \"rank\": 3.731710945608778e-08, \"text\": \"Eccles\", \"types\": [\"Q728937\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eccles_Line\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eccles_Line\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I knew I'd won the fight.\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 645, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am really, really shocked,' a tearful Eccles said after the bout.\", \"from\": 646, \"to\": 713, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 686, \"end\": 692, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eccles_Line\", \"score\": 0.9999999551816937, \"rank\": 3.731710945608778e-08, \"text\": \"Eccles\", \"types\": [\"Q728937\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eccles_Line\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eccles_Line\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'In my mind I won that fight.\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 744, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know what to say other than I am really grateful for everyone that helped me get here.\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 840, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I appreciate you all and I am sorry I could not get it over the line.\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 910, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I knew she was a tricky opponent, but I felt I did the job.\", \"from\": 912, \"to\