limination after Charley Davison fell to defeat against Hatice Akbas.\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1720, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1615, \"end\": 1622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.235603094934759e-14, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}, {\"begin\": 1668, \"end\": 1675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charley_Pollard\", \"score\": 0.7851351479509404, \"rank\": 0.27337737300545567, \"text\": \"Charley\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charley_Pollard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charley_Pollard\"}, {\"begin\": 1707, \"end\": 1713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hatice_Sultan_(daughter_of_Selim_I)\", \"score\": 0.9999999913147803, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hatice\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hatice_Sultan_(daughter_of_Selim_I)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hatice_Sultan_(daughter_of_Selim_I)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 30-year-old, appearing in her second Olympic Games was also on the wrong end of a tight decision.\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1823, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics is no stranger to controversial boxing decisions.\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1887, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2016, Irish fighter Michael Conlan blasted judges after his defeat to Vladimir Nikitin.\", \"from\": 1888, \"to\": 1978, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1897, \"end\": 1902, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_people\", \"score\": 0.7603839919349236, \"rank\": 0.29370073850562817, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_people\"}, {\"begin\": 19